<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Basely" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Basely,</orth> vilely: <cit><quote>they b. fly,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ven 894" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 894</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>b. dignified,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 660" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 660</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>not bought b. with gold,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 1068" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 1068</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the king is not himself, but b. led by flatterers,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 2.1.241" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 II, 1, 241</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. r2 2.1.241" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 II, 1, 241</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 5.2.83" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A V, 2, 83</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 4.5.17" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A IV, 5, 17</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 1.353" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. I, 353</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 1.353" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. I, 353</bibl> <bibl n="shak. tit 4.2.38" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 38</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 5.3.101" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 3, 101</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 5.15.55" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. V, 15, 55</bibl>.
